  <brief_title>This is an Early Study to Investigate the Effect of Gimatecan® in Adults With Solid Tumor</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase I Study of Oral ST1481 Administered Once Weekly Every 3 Out 4 Weeks in Patients With Advanced Solid Malignancies.</official_title>
