  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Gimatecan® is sigma-tau Research's new, potent, oral Topoisomerase I inhibitor. Drugs in this
      class play a crucial role in destroying DNA replication in tumors. We are conducting this
      study to determine the Maximum Tolerated Dose of our compound, when given as a capsule,
      rather than by intravenous injection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
